comment: * Represents a container that manages {@link Dumpable dumpables}.

methods.name: boolean addDumpable(@NonNull Dumpable dumpable)
methods.comment:
* Adds the given {@link Dumpable dumpable} to the container. * *

If a dumpable with the same {@link Dumpable#getDumpableName() name} was added before, this * call is ignored. * * @param dumpable dumpable to be added. * * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the {@link Dumpable#getDumpableName() dumpable name} is * {@code null}. * * @return {@code true} if the dumpable was added, {@code false} if the call was ignored.

methods.name: boolean removeDumpable(@NonNull Dumpable dumpable)
methods.comment:
* Removes the given {@link Dumpable dumpable} from the container.
     *
     * @param dumpable dumpable to be removed.
     *
     * @return {@code true} if the dumpable was removed, {@code false} if it was not previously
     * {@link #addDumpable(Dumpable) added} with the same identify (object reference) and
     * {@link Dumpable#getDumpableName() name}.
